Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count Cruhteo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, his eldest son inherited his title.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Klancain, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have heard that he is intensely\Nloyal to the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have not yet submitted\Nto me are essentially loyalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we can sway him over to our camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it would be possible to get them\Nall to change sides at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The question, though, is whether\Nhe is a man who can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deucalion, lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All ahead dead slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All ahead dead slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now leave the atmosphere\Nand make for the Satellite Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our staging area is Parnassos Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our attack target is\Nthe enemy's moonbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is the main enemy fortress\Nwhere Princess Asseylum is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Given that the Landing Castle in\Nthe sector we are approaching
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is likely to serve as a shelter for Princess\NAsseylum in the event of an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it will be necessary to attack these\Ntwo fortifications simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we will be splitting our\Nforces into two for this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breton Company and the Deucalion will,\Nat 2200 hours Earth Standard Time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,commence their attack\Nagainst the Landing Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After we have confirmation that\Nthe enemy moonbase's forces
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,have split off to defend\Nthe Landing Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trakehner Company will make use of the\Nasteroids that litter the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They will conceal their approach of \Nthe enemy base and then strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This operation is designated Operation Luna Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I had not been so careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, any blame must rest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This entire situation began with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such things, Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were truly gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you had remained asleep, everything\Nwould have gone smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one wept for you...\NAnd he would not have been corrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You care deeply for Slaine, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you?! What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you care for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My heart belongs to the world of Vers\Nand the people who dwell there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I was taught\Nand how I have lived my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will attack the Landing Castle\Nalong with Breton Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are responsible for half\Nof this two-front operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the second being the attack\Non the moonbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is the mission we have\Nbeen given by headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A two-front operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, we're just here to get\Nthe enemy to divide his forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By using this ship as bait again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, I have no intention of\Naccepting that role lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People, don't throw your lives away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and until we return to Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All hands to your assigned stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling you would speak with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to discuss with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I understand it,\Nyou have come all this way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to offer your condolences over\Nmy father, Count Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are quite a long way from Vers, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That, as well as congratulations\Nfor your succession,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are long overdue, Lord Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is I who must apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for failing to congratulate you on your\Nown succession to the peerage, Count Cruhteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Klancain is fine.\NI am still unaccustomed to the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum was looking forward to\Nseeing you again after so long, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that she has been feeling unwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing serious,\Nbut one cannot be too careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am most indebted to your late father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was not hard on you?\NHe was a man who was stern to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a great many lessons from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would not be the man I am today\Nwere it not for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the Tharsis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad that it appears to be of\Nsome use to you, Lord Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard while en route here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something to the effect that you were\Ngoing to found a new kingdom here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was Princess Asseylum's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it also His Majesty's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is my understanding that he is not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our top medical staff are tending to him\Nwith our latest medical equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no cause for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that when Princess\NAsseylum's wish comes true,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His Majesty will also be overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One would hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to lend us your support, Lord Klancain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it would be most reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:08:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To seeing this new kingdom alter Vers' future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Examination of rock clusters \Nexhibiting unnatural behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,suggests objects of different mass behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Camouflage, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Stygis Squadron?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See Count Klancain to a safe location.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy force will be in firing range in 7 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll gradually move the line back\Nas we engage them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and separate the enemy force from the moonbase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All hands to battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now beginning launch sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting flywheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starting catapult arm rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Opening hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clydesdale Platoon, move to launch position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger. Clydesdale Leader to all units.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move to launch position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anchors engaged.\NCatapult arm rotation nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beginning acceleration.\NGo for launch in 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clydesdale Leader, cleared for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger, cleared for launch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All units, launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blast off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now Mustang Platoon, prepare for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Breton Company and Deucalion,\Nbegin attack as planned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that. Let's go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Begin attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple enemy contacts detected in\Nthe direction of Libra. Kataphrakts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Intercept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy defenses are\Npretty tough, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They knew that this\Nwas going to be a tough fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reason it was necessary to push ahead\Nwith this operation in spite of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...was because HQ had a more\Nimportant mission in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The captain was right to be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a covert infiltration by an assault team \Nduring an all-out offensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For sabotage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, there would be no need\Nfor secrecy then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their objective has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to assassinate Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}90 seconds to closest approach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger. Let's stick to the plan, then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had wanted to come alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be dangerous from here on. So–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, come on... You're giving me that again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The captain assigned me to provide support
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,out of recognition for my accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the fact that I've been fighting\Nalongside you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is close enough.\NI'll make the drop from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous. We're still too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy units!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Drop me!\NYou can't return fire like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! The wind's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can dodge it from this range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inko!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuki. It's safe to drop me, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split up here.\NEach team will search their assigned route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When the target is spotted,\Ncarry out mission immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was also expecting an infiltration team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is likely that the enemy\Nhas also infiltrated other zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will dispatch guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The princesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being relocated to a more secure block.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Troyard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your servant Barouhcruz has rushed\Nover to provide assistance!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you have come.\NYou have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will also send Harklight to your location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold them off here.\NThe rest of you, locate the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Importing base security feeds and generating map.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using you too much, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm all right...\NInfiltration team position confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I follow their path of advance...\Nthat's where Seylum will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this.\NThe enemy is as good as wiped–
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra high-tension monofilament\Nwire spooled around
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a superconducting\Nelectromagnetic bobbin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that this blade\Ncannot cut through!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You see to the rats in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir Harklight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Consider it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Target located!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:16:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Slaine, we've lost contact with the escorts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Where are the princesses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making for the landing port,\Nbut enemy forces are heading there as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sending more personnel immed–
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need a reason to save someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such arrogance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The suffering of those you save\Nnever enters your mind, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady Lemrina!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me.\NI will remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We must escape at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Escape to where?\NAnd from whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain we can find safety–
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place is my only shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:17:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we? Do...\NDo another search. Seylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...has to be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see you here, Inaho Kaizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slaine Troyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calculate firing point from bullet path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thermograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Steam pipes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Seylum...\NWhere is Princess Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get her involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get her involved?\NShe is a means to achieving my ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to exploit her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she is, do you have a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were an enemy all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you were, there would have \Nbeen no need to hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eddelrittuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Eddelrittuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seylum... I'm glad... you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ina–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum Vers Allusia,\Nidentity confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thought processes stopped.\NRunning backup program.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Temporarily assuming control\Nover Inaho Kaizuka's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thought processes, awareness,\Nand speech functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this boy is aware that\NPrincess Asseylum is a separate individual,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he misidentifies her as a part of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part of himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He therefore placed maximum priority\Non her safety and has acted to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He came... to rescue me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will provide information in accordance\Nwith those behavioral principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use communications line\Ninside F3 gate airlock
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to contact Inko Amifumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The crew of the Deucalion...\Nthey are here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Milady.\NI know where that airlock is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't leave Inaho here–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no cause for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In 420 seconds, help will arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should hurry all the more.\NThere is no telling if that "help" is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell him something for me.\N"Thank you from the bottom of my heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Command confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also think of you as a part of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I have one more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment, I'll get the transmission–
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you unharmed, Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Klancain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We last met at my father's commendation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored that you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:10.00,T1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chance Meeting and Separation
